@@dASSASSIN@@W

Assassins are patient executioners. They win by controlling first contact,
creating one lethal opening, and ending the fight before opponents can answer.

@@dPassive class advantages@@W
  * @@wExtra attack round@@W while Assassin remort is active.
  * @@wCritical chance@@W bonus (+0.05% per level, up to +5% at 100).
  * @@wCritical damage@@W bonus (+0.2% per level, up to +20% at 100).
  * @@wBackstab / circle damage@@W bonus (+1% per level, up to +100% at 100).

@@dUnique Assassin mechanics@@W
  * Access to @@wAssassin stance@@W and @@wNinja stance@@W at higher remort level.
  * Core opener class for stealth burst and positional kill windows.
  * Uses @@wDexterity@@W as prime remort attribute.

@@dAssassin reincarnation bonuses@@W
  * @@wAssassin + Warlock remort reincarnations >= 20@@W unlocks
    @@wDual Wield@@W permanently.

See also: @@mremort stance ninja warlock nightblade reincarnate@@W
